data.description: SELLER APPROVED INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN for qualified buyers! This charming home offers a unique opportunity to live on .45 acres just 3 miles from Ed Walline Beach Access. The mother-in-law suite and upstairs studio make it perfect for rentals or multi-generational living. With a total of 6 bedrooms and 5.5 bathrooms and over 4300 sqft, there is plenty of space for everyone. Recent upgrades include newer HVAC and water heaters.84 Vota stands out with its rental potential and versatility. Whether you're looking for additional income or a separate space for extended family members, the backhouse/mother-in-law suite and upstairs studio offer versatility and flexibility.
